RESULTANT_TRADE   ----> 

RESULTANT_TRADE} - Event type for resultant trade ("101") --> a new trade generated as a result of a previous trade lifecycle action (exercise / assignment / closeout).
Your flow simplified:
Buy to Open option trade
Trade goes to HILD
Trade corrected â†’ LIVE
Exercise / Assignment
Original trade â†’ CLOSED
System allows new trade creation
ğŸ”‘ That new trade is created with Event Type = 101

A resultant trade is:
A trade created because something happened to another trade
Not created independently by a dealer




Reverse Trade  --> 
In real banking systems:
You cannot delete a trade
You cannot overwrite history

ğŸ‘‰ You must reverse it

ğŸ¦ Real-World Analogy (Non-Banking)
